The paper proposes a revenue management system for air-cargo that combines machine learning prediction with decision-making using mathematical optimization methods. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science), and cs.IT (Information Theory). However, given the focus on machine learning and optimization, cs.LG and cs.AI are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also discusses data cleaning, which could place it in cs.DS. Finally, the application of the proposed system to a commercial airline company suggests that it could also belong to cs.CE or cs.IT.
